headline: Quest Diagnostics Names Adrienne Brott Senior Vice President and Chief Quality and Regulatory Affairs Officer
summary: Quest Diagnostics (NYSE: DGX), a leading provider of diagnostic information services, today announced that Adrienne L. Brott, an accomplished quality and regulatory affairs healthcare leader, has been named senior vice president and chief quality and regulatory affairs officer.
